## Project Rules

- Use React 18 with TypeScript strict mode
- Use Supabase for backend (no custom API)
- Mobile-first design (min-width: 375px)
- All text must use i18next (no hardcoded strings)
- Use Tailwind utility classes only
- Database operations through Supabase client
- All mutations must respect RLS policies
- Use React Query for data fetching
- Implement optimistic updates for better UX
- Handle errors with toast notifications
- Use Zustand for global state (auth, language, theme)
- Follow Airbnb TypeScript style guide
